    "For zeroshot stance detection (ZSSD) on C-STANCE, transformer-based models such as RoBERTa and XLNet have set new benchmarks, surpassing RNN-based models and underscoring the complexity of claim target prediction in terms of F1-score as well (Zhao et al. 2023).",
